Friday, February 25, 1994

DISCIPLINARY DOCKET

92-1340. Dayton Bar Assn. v. McDonald.

It is ordered by the court, sua sponte, effective February 22,1994, that Michael J. McDonald, Attorney Registration No. 0022740, last known business address in Miamisburg, Ohio, is found in contempt for failure to comply with this court’s order of April 27, 1993.
